value.title: 5 Key Takeaways from Anthropic’s Latest Economic Index: Prompting Is Still Critical, AI Can Handle Massive Tasks If You Break Them Up, and Deskilling is a Bigger Issue Than Unemployment
value.content: Anthropic just released their fourth Economic Index report—2 million conversations analyzed across Claude.ai and their API.  Some of this we know, but Anthropic has the data. My top takeaways:  #1. AI Helps Your Best People the Most, Not Your Junior Staff.  The Data Confirms It. You hear this from so many top CTOs: senior engineers... Continue Reading
